行后怎么验证
先在你同事的 PG 里查回填结果，例如回填近 3 天：
SELECT stat_date, COUNT(*) AS rows_cnt, ROUND(SUM(spend), 2) AS total_spend
FROM facebook_ads_daily_export
WHERE stat_date >= current_date - 3
GROUP BY stat_date
ORDER BY stat_date DESC;
如果你这次主要是补 2026-04-19、2026-04-20、2026-04-21，也可以更精确地查：
SELECT stat_date, COUNT(*) AS rows_cnt, ROUND(SUM(spend), 2) AS total_spend
FROM facebook_ads_daily_export
WHERE stat_date IN ('2026-04-19', '2026-04-20', '2026-04-21')
GROUP BY stat_date
ORDER BY stat_date;
补充说明
如果你不是想“近 N 天”，而是只补某一个固定日期，直接用底层脚本更合适：
cd /root/work/FB-Ad-Logic-Engine
set -a
. ./.env.pg
set +a
node server/scripts/export-facebook-to-pg.js --date=2026-04-20
